HEADWORD: Whoreson
<hw>Whore"son</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A bastard;
colloquially, a low, scurvy fellow; -- used generally in contempt, or in
coarse humor. Also used adjectively.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whorish</ent>⟦br⟧
